text: National Cheng Hsing University (NCHU; ) is a university in Taiwan. It was name "Chung Hsing (中興)" meaning "Chinese national revival". The main campus is in Taichung City. It was founded in 1919. NCHU is among the four universities of the Taiwan Comprehensive University System. ==Other websites== *Xīng Dà C Category:1919 establishments in Asia Category:20th-century establishments in Taiwan
